## US.14 As a student, I want to receive reminders about events I've registered for so that I don't miss them


## Steps and expected results 

1. Create a new student account using a valid email address you have access to.

2. Click on Browse Events in the sidebar , this will show you a list of all upcoming events.

3. Click on any event in the list to open its information page.

4. Click on the Save Event button to register/save the event.

5. After saving the event, click on the Email button on the event page.  
   This triggers the reminder/confirmation email for that event.

6. Open the inbox of the email address used for the student account and check the received email.

### Expected results
- A confirmation/reminder email is sent after clicking the Email button.
- The email includes:
  - The event title
  - The event ID
  - The event date, time, and location
